Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:05.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You are being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:05.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你被監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The government has a secret system--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,政府有一套秘密設備…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,a machine that spies on you every hour of every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一台每時每刻監視你的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I designed the machine to detect acts of terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我設計這個機器偵測恐怖行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but it sees everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但它卻看到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:19.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Violent crimes involving ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:19.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,普通人捲入的暴力犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The government considers these people irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,政府認為這些人無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.42,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.42,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們不敢茍同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:28.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hunted by the authorities, we work in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:28.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,為逃避官方追捕，我們秘密行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.59,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You will never find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.59,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你不可能找到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.59,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But victim or perpetrator,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.59,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但無論是受害者還是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,if your number's up, we'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一旦你的號碼出現，我們就會找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,大熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:00.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:00.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不，不，不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He found the treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他找到獎勵零食了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Come on. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,行了，別這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:07.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He's a military working dog, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:07.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他是只軍犬，芬奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Search and rescue,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,搜索和營救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:12.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,trained to track people, uncover explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:12.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,受訓跟蹤敵人，查找爆炸物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:15.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I suppose Moliere is no challenge at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:15.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,莫裏哀完全不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:19.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have Bear track down Ms. Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:19.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許我該讓大熊跟蹤肖女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I thought you put her on the new number.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我以為你給她新號碼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I did, but communication is not her strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我是給了，不過她不喜歡聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:25.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Tally-ho, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:25.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,出現了，芬奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Our engineer's in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們的工程師出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:29.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,These turbine blades are missing a customs clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:29.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這些渦輪葉片還沒報關
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,As soon as they get to Kenya,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一運到肯尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.58,eng_1,,0,0,0,,the locals will demand a bribe to clear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.58,chs_2,,0,0,0,,當地海關要索賄才會同意入關
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But, since we're out of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不過現在我們時間不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,call Benny at the Mombasa customs house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,打給蒙巴薩海關的本尼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:40.36,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Tell him there's a bottle of Kentucky bourbon</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:40.36,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>跟他說這裏有一瓶</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>with his name on it.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>印著他名字的波旁酒</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:46.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Our girl's got more foreign contacts than Reese and I combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:46.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這妹子的外國聯繫人比我和裏斯加起來還多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:49.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Indeed. Maria Martinez is quite the world traveler.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:49.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>那當然，瑪麗亞·馬丁內斯蹤跡遍及全球</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:52.87,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Masters in engineering from Stanford.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:52.87,chs_2,,0,0,0,,斯坦福大學的工程學碩士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:56.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She works for Hydral Corp, a private energy company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:56.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她在水力公司工作，一家私營能源企業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's currently working on reconstruction projects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她當前正在第三世界國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:00.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,in third-world countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:00.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,開展改建工程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.61,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She digs wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.61,chs_2,,0,0,0,,挖井？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:06.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Builds multimillion-dollar generators is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:06.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,建造數百萬美元級別的發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Her last project was replacing the generators
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:08.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她上一項工程是替換伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:11.12,eng_1,,0,0,0,,inside a hydroelectric dam in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:11.12,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一座水電大壩的發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:12.89,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:12.89,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:14.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Great work here, adding the GPS trackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:14.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮，加上了GPS追蹤器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Considering everything we went through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們費盡千辛萬苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,to get those generators into the country and assemble them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,才把發電機送入境再組裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.10,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Can't afford to lose anything, like we did in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.10,chs_2,,0,0,0,,絕對不能像伊拉克那樣再丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:24.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We have to make sure our supply chain and sources are beyond reproach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:24.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,必須確保供應鏈和來源絕對安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>That's Ken Davis, Maria's boss.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>這是肯·戴維斯，瑪麗亞的老闆</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>He runs Hydral Corp.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,</i>水力公司是他開的</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I have to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我得接個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Hello?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>喂？</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Hello.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>你好</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.42,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>The package is ready.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.42,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>包裹準備就緒</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But we can't talk on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但我們不能在電話裏談
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Meet at the usual place <i>in an hour.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一小時後老地方見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:46.59,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:46.59,chs_2,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Didn't see that comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,真是出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria just took a five-finger discount on a GPS tracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞順手牽走了一個GPS追蹤器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.81,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Just a meeting with a supplier I forgot about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.81,chs_2,,0,0,0,,忘了會見一個供應商
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Mm, okay. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 好吧\N- 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.61,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And she lied to her boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.61,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她對老闆說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Plus this delivery of a mysterious package?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,外加那個待交付的神秘包裹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sounds like pre-operational tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,像是一次預演戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Tactics? Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,戰術？什麼戰術？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,A terrorist cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,恐怖小組的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.78,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If Maria were a relevant number,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.78,chs_2,,0,0,0,,如果瑪麗亞是相關號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.92,eng_1,,0,0,0,,she would fall under the government's purview.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.92,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她會進入政府的管轄範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maybe the machine got its wires crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許機器電線搭錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Ever since it's had that cochlear cuckoo on speed dial--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,才會把那只壞耳蝸的布谷鳥列入聯繫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I fail to see how its relationship with Ms. Groves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我沒看出葛洛弗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,has anything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,與機器的關係對此有何影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.16,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that our number could be a terrorist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.16,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你真認為這個號碼會是恐怖分子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.97,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I believe Shaw's gonna need our backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.97,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我認為肖需要我們支援
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.77,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Hello, Harold.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.77,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>你好，哈羅德</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You wanted to talk to me? Or her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你想跟我談？還是跟她？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.34,eng_1,,0,0,0,,How did you-- Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.34,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼…算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>I was curious--</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>我很好奇…</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about your little number, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我對你那小號碼一無所知，哈羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>I'm pursing</i> <i>a much larger objective.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>我關心的是一個大得多的目標</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The chip that Decima stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,德西瑪公司偷走的芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.32,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Has the machine directed you to--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.32,chs_2,,0,0,0,,機器指示你去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That chip has already been back-engineered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那個芯片已經被破解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and thousands of copies are being generated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們說話這會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,已經復製出成千上萬個了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.73,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Enough to run Samaritan <i>at full power.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.73,chs_2,,0,0,0,,</i>足夠讓撒瑪利亞全負荷運轉</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The machine has alerted me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,機器已經警告我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,that our elusive adversary is back in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們神出鬼沒的對手回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Eliminating him might be our last chance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,除掉他可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.81,eng_1,,0,0,0,,at stopping Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.81,chs_2,,0,0,0,,終止撒瑪利亞的最後機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.81,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'll be in touch the next time my ear starts burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.81,chs_2,,0,0,0,,等我下次耳朵癢了再聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.81,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Do you have my position?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.81,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你知道我的位置嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I've made a new friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我交了個新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but I'm not feeling particularly sociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但我現在不是很想寒暄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.59,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Have our asset at Parkhurst Security go blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.59,chs_2,,0,0,0,,把我們在帕克赫斯特安保的設備關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:51.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:51.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:55.35,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:55.35,chs_2,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,A little volume, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,來點聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:16.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:16.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Going dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,隱蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:22.61,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Rendezvous in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:22.61,chs_2,,0,0,0,,兩分鐘後見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:33.28,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What the hell, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:33.28,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼，女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:38.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thought you were my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:38.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,還以為你是我叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Beirut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,貝魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Baghdad. - Baghdad for masguf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 巴格達\N- 巴格達烤魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Saddam knew his fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,薩達姆很懂魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,說的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.37,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But shawarma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.37,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不過切片烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.51,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Beirut, hands down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.51,chs_2,,0,0,0,,貝魯特多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.52,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm doing everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.52,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我能做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They won't release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們不放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We must do something now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們得做點什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.52,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I traced Maria's earlier phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.52,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我監聽了瑪麗亞之前的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Jamal Risha is an Iraqi who immigrated to the US
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,賈馬爾·瑞捨是伊拉克人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,兩年前移民到美國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,This man, he won't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這個人，他不見我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He won't even talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他甚至不跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He's the only thing blocking Omar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就是他困住了奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.80,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave my brother behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.80,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不能丟下我兄弟不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Finch, you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,芬奇，聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,According to the Immigration and Customs Enforcement database,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,根據移民局和海關數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.61,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar Risha was detained by the Department Of Homeland Security
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.61,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾·瑞捨一周前到達肯尼迪國際機場後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.98,eng_1,,0,0,0,,after landing at JFK a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.98,chs_2,,0,0,0,,被國土安全局扣留了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Where are they holding him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,現在他們把他關在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,A high-security detention center in Manhattan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,曼哈頓的一個高度安全拘留中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,under special administrative measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,實行特殊行政管制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Those are reserved for terrorism suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這是關押恐怖活動嫌疑人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:46.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We have a small window of opportunity to make an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:46.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們能起作用的希望很小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:55.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,This should open their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:55.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這個能讓他們開開眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.67,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Big bombs keep coming in little packages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.67,chs_2,,0,0,0,,小包裹裏都是大炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Like the shoe bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就像扔鞋彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,好運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.98,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jamal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.98,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝，賈馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'll keep eyes on Jamal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我盯著賈馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,See if he has any other contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,看看他還跟誰聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.65,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'll stick close to our friend Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.65,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我繼續盯緊我們的瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:15.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Figure out what the hell she's gotten herself into.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:15.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,看看她到底趟了什麼渾水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But why do you gotta drag me all the way up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但是你幹嘛費老大勁把我拽來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.93,eng_1,,0,0,0,,just to watch your girl snap a few memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.93,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就為了看姑娘拍留念照呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.10,eng_1,,0,0,0,,When's the last time you saw a New Yorker from The Village
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.10,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候見過紐約市民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,take tourist photos at the UN?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,來聯合國拍留念照？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,說得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.67,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If you're so smart, what do you need me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.67,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你這麼聰明，拉我過來幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You can't park here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這裏不准停車！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.34,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Security precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.34,chs_2,,0,0,0,,安全防範
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.78,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.78,chs_2,,0,0,0,,嗯，我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Way to make yourself useful, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,發揮你用處的時候到了，萊諾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:54.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You know, I don't understand all the hoopla with the UN anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:54.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不理解聯合國干的那些破事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Bunch of silver-spoon</i> <i>bureaucrats, if you ask me.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>一群出身貴族的官僚</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And don't even get me started
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,更別提那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,with the extraterritorial privileges either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,什麼治外法權了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I should've just stolen a badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我真該偷個警徽過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,How many countries you think there are in the UN?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你覺得聯合國裏有多少國家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.43,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Like 50-something? - 193.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.43,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 大概50個？\N- 193個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.10,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You know, you really should get out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.10,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你真該多出去走走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Learn something about other cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,多學學其他文化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這算什麼話？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:10.97,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I just ate a falafel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:10.97,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我剛吃了個中東三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and you got some on your tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是啊，還有些留在領帶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.47,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's the second tie this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.47,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這周的第二條領帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:19.61,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria's taking photos of the interior of the UN compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:19.61,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞給聯合國廣場內部拍了照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:24.32,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Surveillance is the last planning stage before an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:24.32,chs_2,,0,0,0,,監視是進攻前最後的步驟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's not shooting the compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她不是在拍聯合國廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:32.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's taking pictures of this <i>guy.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:32.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她在拍這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Photo's on its way, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,照片傳過去了，芬奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.44,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't know who the suit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.44,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不認識這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The man in the photo is Rene Lapointe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,照片裏的人叫雷內·拉普安特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.97,eng_1,,0,0,0,,a French diplomat and current United Nations High Commissioner for refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.97,chs_2,,0,0,0,,法國外交官，也是聯合國難民署高級專員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.34,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He's responsible for approving the asylum request
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.34,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他負責批准賈馬爾兄弟奧馬爾的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,of Jamal's brother Omar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,政治避難請求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:58.98,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He just triggered our Jihad Jane to go live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:58.98,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他剛剛激活了我們的聖戰分子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.92,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Maria just stopped his car.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.92,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>瑪麗亞截住了他的車</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's putting something--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她放了什麼東西上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Miss Shaw, what is it?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>肖女士，什麼東西？</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.26,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Oh, that was smooth.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.26,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>動作真是流暢啊</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>I couldn't have done</i> <i>that better myself.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>我也不過如此</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She just placed the GPS tracker onto Lapointe's limo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她剛在拉普安特豪車上放了GPS追蹤器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:20.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>She's tracking him.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:20.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>她在跟蹤他</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.21,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.21,chs_2,,0,0,0,,出租車！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>And, more importantly...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>更重要的是…</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:29.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I think we just identified her target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:29.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我想我們已經找到她的目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,All these fat-cat diplomats travel all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這些有權有勢的外交官拿著別人的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,eatin' on someone else's dime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,周遊世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,while they talk about feeding the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,還滿嘴說著要救濟窮人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:48.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maybe you ought to consider applying for a passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:48.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許你可以考慮辦個護照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.22,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I have a passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.22,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我有護照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,My ex and I went to Saint Thomas for our honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我前妻和我去聖托馬斯島度的蜜月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:57.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You mean the US Virgin Islands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:57.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你是說美國的維爾京群島？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.87,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's our girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.87,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們的姑娘來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Your engineer pulls one hell of a changing act.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>你的工程師換衣服可真快</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Yeah, dressed to kill.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>嗯，光鮮亮麗去殺人</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.71,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's still got that package in her shoulder bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.71,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那個包裹還在她包裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, I'll watch the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,去吧，我守著前門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We might have a problem, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,可能有麻煩了，芬奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:49.65,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Maria's closing in on her target.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:49.65,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>瑪麗亞正在接近她的目標</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You want proof? There's proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你想要證據？這就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right, Ms. Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一切還好嗎，肖女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,False alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,虛驚一場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Unless we're worried about paper cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,大不了就是被紙割傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我們認識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar Risha is not a terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾·瑞捨不是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He worked for US forces in Iraq
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他為駐伊美軍工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and for my company as a translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也是我們公司的翻譯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,There's a recommendation in here from my boss Ken Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這是我老闆肯·戴維斯的推薦信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:12.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What more proof do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:12.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你還想要什麼證據？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我猜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- You must be Maria? - In person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 你一定是瑪麗亞？\N- 正是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.44,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria, the US Department Of Homeland Security
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.44,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞，美國國土安全局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.71,eng_1,,0,0,0,,has asked me to weigh all the evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.71,chs_2,,0,0,0,,要求我在給避難者分級前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,before classifying refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,慎重權衡所有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.51,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What evidence do you have to the contrary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.51,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你有什麼反面證據？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That is confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這是機密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But, let me assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但是，我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar Risha will have a fair hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾·瑞捨會得到公平審訊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Now if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Look, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Just tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,直接告訴我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,what's the going rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,需要多少錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你瘋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I am not leaving until I get an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你不回答我就不走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.37,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Security! - Excuse me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.37,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 保安！\N- 抱歉，女士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.73,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.73,chs_2,,0,0,0,,請跟我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉，先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.37,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.37,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她跟我一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,沒關係，我認識她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.98,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Allow me to take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.98,chs_2,,0,0,0,,請讓我來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.65,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.65,chs_2,,0,0,0,,芬奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria was about to get tossed out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞剛要被趕出去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:07.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,when this guy stepped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:07.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這個人插手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You work with Ken Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你跟肯·戴維斯共事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.36,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.36,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.93,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna burden you with my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.93,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不想讓你負擔我的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:15.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:15.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,My former interpreter from Iraq
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我的前任翻譯是伊拉克人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,is being held on suspicion of terrorism
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,現在被懷疑是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and might be deported.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,可能會被驅逐出境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:25.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I know it's a false allegation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:25.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我知道這項指控不成立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.67,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But that jerk won't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.67,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但那個混蛋不信我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:30.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Monsieur Lapointe may be lazy, even corrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:30.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,拉普安特先生可能懶散，甚至貪污
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but you don't get all that power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但他那些權力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,by being a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也不是好人能得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,There are ways around men like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,對他這種人可以採取其他辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.22,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.22,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不知道還能做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許我能幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Without companies</i> <i>like Hydral Corp</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>少了水力公司這種</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,that build infrastructure,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,建造公共設施的企業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:46.36,eng_1,,0,0,0,,the United Nations would never accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:46.36,chs_2,,0,0,0,,聯合國就無法有任何作為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, some of the old guard prefer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不幸的是，一些保守派
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>to bite the hand that feeds.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>反而恩將仇報</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.44,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Let me make a few calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.44,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我要打幾個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If you need anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,如果你有任何需要的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.47,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.47,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Looks like Maria just found herself a white knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,看來瑪麗亞找到救星了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Christos Sevon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,克裏斯托·斯萬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:07.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,A career diplomat from Greece currently serving
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:07.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是希臘的職業外交官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,on the UN Sustainable Energy program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,目前為聯合國可持續能源計劃效力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He raises funds to support reconstruction projects
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他為改建工程籌集基金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:15.59,eng_1,,0,0,0,,like the one Maria worked on in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:15.59,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就像瑪麗亞在伊拉克做的那種工程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.89,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Well, he's offered to help get Omar into the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.89,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他主動幫助奧馬爾入境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.26,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Let's hope that he doesn't live to regret that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.26,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但願他不會後悔做這個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We need to get a look at that evidence against Omar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們得看到不利於奧馬爾的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.73,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sounds like Omar could use a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.73,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾貌似需要一名好律師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's time Mr. Reese and I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許我和裏斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:31.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,did a little pro bono work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:31.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也該做些公益工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,How can I help you and your associates,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有什麼可以幫助您和合夥人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kingfisher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,金費捨先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:40.28,eng_1,,0,0,0,,My firm represents several refugees
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:40.28,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我的公司代表若干在伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.58,eng_1,,0,0,0,,who worked for the US government in Iraq
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.58,chs_2,,0,0,0,,為美國政府工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,now seeking asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,現在尋求庇護的避難者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:45.28,eng_1,,0,0,0,,There are concerns about refugees from Iraq
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:45.28,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們對伊拉克難民申請移民美國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.59,eng_1,,0,0,0,,immigrating to the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.59,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有一些顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're-- we're aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是的，我們…我們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,One of our clients-- Omar Risha--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我的一個客戶，奧馬爾·瑞捨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:54.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,is being detained for alleged links to terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:54.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,由於所謂的「與恐怖主義有聯繫」正被拘留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.36,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I know Monsieur Risha's case well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.36,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我很瞭解瑞捨先生的案子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:14:01.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,In fact, I have to make a final decision on it this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:14:01.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,其實，我們在這周內就要對此案做最終決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我可以看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If I'm to prepare a legal defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,如果要準備辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.21,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I require all of the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.21,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我需要瞭解所有事實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.81,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You may review it, but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.81,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你可以看，但只能在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I received that letter from the Iraqi government last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我上周從伊拉克政府收到此信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.22,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The Ministry of the Interior say they have proof
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.22,chs_2,,0,0,0,,內政部聲稱他們有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,that Omar is involved in terrorist activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,證明奧馬爾參與了恐怖主義活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.12,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.12,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:28.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Um, the Ministry of the Interior is hardly reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:28.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,內政部不是很可靠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It's full of former Shia militia members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很多成員都是前什葉派民兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.13,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They view Iraqis that helped American forces
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.13,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們認為幫助美軍的伊拉克人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,as traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, two terrorists
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,三年前，兩個曾在伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,who killed US soldiers in Iraq
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,殺害美軍士兵的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.90,eng_1,,0,0,0,,were discovered living in Bowling Green, Kentucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.90,chs_2,,0,0,0,,被發現居住在肯塔基州鮑林格林市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They fooled Immigration officials
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們假扮翻譯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,by posing as former interpreters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,騙過了移民局官員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.34,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yes, but, surely, such an isolated case
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.34,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是的，但是這種單個案例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:50.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,should not affect the plight of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:50.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也不該影響數千人的處境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to put my signature
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我承擔不起在一個潛在恐怖分子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,on an application of a potential terrorist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,申請表上簽字的後果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.85,eng_1,,0,0,0,,however small the probability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:56.85,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不管其可能性有多小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.52,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If one more terrorist slips through,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.52,chs_2,,0,0,0,,再漏過一個恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:02.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,it will jeopardize all the other refugees seeking asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:02.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就會危害其他所有尋求庇護的避難者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.49,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.49,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你要理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Understood.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>我理解</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Thank you for your time. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 感謝您的寶貴時間\N- 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:21.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Well, it's difficult to determine the authenticity of the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:21.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很難確定這封信的真實性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Any new developments</i> <i>on your end, Ms. Shaw?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>你那邊有新進展嗎，肖女士？</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She takes the 7 train to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她坐7點的車回了家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Does that help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這有用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Jamal, good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,賈馬爾，好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.22,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I found someone in a position we can leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.22,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我發現一個對我們有用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Call me back, and I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,回電話，我再給你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.73,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.73,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- How many extra mags you got? - Extra mags? You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 你有多少額外彈夾？\N- 額外彈夾？你沒搞錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.71,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Finch, we're gonna need some backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.71,chs_2,,0,0,0,,芬奇，我們需要支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:05.92,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:05.92,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Personally, I prefer potassium chloride to chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我個人認為氯化鉀比氯仿更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:16.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Acts quicker and no trace in postmortem toxicology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:16.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,見效更快，屍體不留痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:27.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And the other thing about chloroform, it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:27.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,而且氯仿還有個缺點，就是很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.98,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Who the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.98,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這人到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,French Algerian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,法裔阿爾及利亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,With a Maserin bolt knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,帶著一把馬賽裏彈簧刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.85,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'd say French Foreign Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.85,chs_2,,0,0,0,,肯定是法國外籍兵團的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You've made friends all over the world, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你的朋友真是遍佈全球，瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Foreign Legion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,外籍兵團？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why would they wanna kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們為什麼要殺我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't speak French.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不知道，我又不懂法語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.49,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Finch, what's our ETA on Captain America?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.49,chs_2,,0,0,0,,芬奇，我們的美國隊長什麼時候能到？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:50.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Mr. Reese should be with you directly.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:50.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>裏斯先生會直接去你那</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.87,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Stay close to the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.87,chs_2,,0,0,0,,緊貼牆邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:57.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing this guy might have some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:57.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我猜這人可能還有幾個同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:08.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Guess that falafel didn't slow you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:08.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,看來三明治沒讓你身手變慢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Is that it? Any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就這些？還有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:11.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:11.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞，趴下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.80,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Your boy there's got issues.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.80,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>你哥們有問題吧</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.58,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hope that guy has health insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.58,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但願那人有醫保
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What's up with the Evel Knievel stunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那招特技表演哪兒學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They didn't teach you that in Marine jump school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你在海軍跳傘學校沒學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Only if a 5-cent piece of lead won't get you out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,只是小線索就不勞你出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- But thanks for coming. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 多謝前來\N- 不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:01.51,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt, but who the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:01.51,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉打斷下，你們又是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We're a lot like you, Ms. Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們跟你很像，馬丁內斯女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.52,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We help people in less fortunate circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.52,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們幫助不走運的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.92,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>We only require one thing</i> <i>in return for our services.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.92,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>我們只求一個回報</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.12,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.12,chs_2,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:14.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:14.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,實話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:18.59,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to get Omar Risha into the US?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:18.59,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要幫奧馬爾·瑞捨來美國？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar was my interpreter on my last project.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾是我做上個項目的翻譯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.37,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We were in a convoy transporting six generators
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.37,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們護送轉移六台發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,from Kuwait to Iraq when we were ambushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,從科威特轉到伊拉克時被伏擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I jumped into a ditch, about to be overrun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我跳進壕溝裏，就要被擊敗的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.47,eng_1,,0,0,0,,when Omar jumped in next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.47,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾跳到我旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and shot two of the terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,開槍打了兩個恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The rest fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,其餘的逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.78,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.78,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:43.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sounds like he deserves a medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:43.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,應該獎勵塊金牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.85,eng_1,,0,0,0,,After I left Iraq,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.85,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我離開伊拉克後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar started receiving death threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾開始收到死亡恐嚇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If he's sent back, he'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,如果他被送回去，他會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What do French legionnaires have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,法國外籍兵團跟這事有什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The day before Omar left, he wanted to talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾離開前一天，他想找我談談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,about some generators that went missing in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,關於在伊拉克丟的幾台發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.80,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He didn't wanna talk about it on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.80,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他不想在電話裏說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The Iraqi Ministry of the Interior
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,伊拉克內政部寄了這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,sent this letter to the UN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,給聯合國
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.21,eng_1,,0,0,0,,stating that Omar has links to terrorist groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.21,chs_2,,0,0,0,,說奧馬爾跟恐怖組織有關
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,This is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.32,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why would someone do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.32,chs_2,,0,0,0,,為什麼有人要這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.85,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Detective Fusco arrested the injured legionnaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.85,chs_2,,0,0,0,,法斯克警探逮捕了受傷的兵團士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, when he wakes up, he can answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許他醒了之後，可以回答這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:26.42,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They could be working for a foreign intelligence service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:26.42,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們可能是為某個國外情報局工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They could also be working
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也可能是為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,for the UN High Commissioner Lapointe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,聯合國高級專員拉普安特工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,His last post
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他的上個職位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,was head of UN peacekeeping in the Congo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是剛果的聯合國維和首腦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.93,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Among the units under his control
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.93,chs_2,,0,0,0,,在他控制之下的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,was a company of French legionnaires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就有一家法國外籍兵團公司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why would Lapointe wanna kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,為什麼拉普安特要殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.67,eng_1,,0,0,0,,for trying to help Omar get into the US?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.67,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就因為幫奧馬爾入境？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We need to talk to Omar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們得跟奧馬爾談談
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He could shed some light on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他也許能解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.68,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.68,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He's being held incommunicado.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他被拘留，禁止通信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:50.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We can't even trust his government-appointed lawyer to deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:50.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不能信任他的政府委派律師去傳息兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:54.78,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll talk to his new representation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:54.78,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許他可以跟他的新代表說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.54,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Like I told my last attorney, I'm not talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.54,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我跟上任律師也說過我不會跟你交談的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.71,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We're not with the government, Mr. Risha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.71,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們不是政府的人，瑞捨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We're friends of Maria Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們是瑪麗亞·馬丁內斯的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.78,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you work with the people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.78,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許你跟那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,that are setting me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一起串通陷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria told us how you saved her life in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞告訴我們你在伊拉克救她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.12,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I don't have more proof,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.12,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我沒有更多證據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但我們時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Last night, a team of legionnaires
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,昨晚，一隊外籍兵團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,made an attempt on Maria's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,想要取瑪麗亞的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.89,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.89,chs_2,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Is she okay? - She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 她還好嗎？\N- 她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And she's in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她現在在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But there was something important
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你們上次談話時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,you wanted to tell Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你說有重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:49.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,during your last conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:49.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,想告訴瑪麗亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:52.44,eng_1,,0,0,0,,About the generators.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:52.44,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那些發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The ones at the energy project
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她在伊拉克做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:58.35,eng_1,,0,0,0,,that she worked on in Iraq?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:58.35,chs_2,,0,0,0,,能源工程的發電機？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:01.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,After Maria left,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:01.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞離開之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,the generators were never installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,發電機沒有安裝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:07.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The hydroelectric plant failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:07.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,水電站關閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The entire province went dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,整個省都停電了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hospitals had no electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,醫院沒有電
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Patients died on operating tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,病人死在手術台上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The local police lost control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,當地警察控制不住局面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Within a week, Al-Qaeda moved back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一星期之內，基地組織就捲土重來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:21.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What happened to the generators?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:21.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,發電機發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to tell Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那就是我想告訴瑪麗亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:27.34,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Right before I left, I translated a contract
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:27.34,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就在我離開前，我翻譯了一份合同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,for the transportation of six generators.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,關於轉移六台發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:34.61,eng_1,,0,0,0,,A contract signed by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:34.61,chs_2,,0,0,0,,誰簽署的合同？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can protect Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你確定你能保護瑪麗亞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼問？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.22,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Because it was her boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.22,chs_2,,0,0,0,,因為是她老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Ken Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,肯·戴維斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:46.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Davis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:46.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,戴維斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why would he ship generators all the way to Iraq
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他為什麼把發電機一路運到伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,only to turn around and ship them somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,轉而又運到其他地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:53.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maybe he got a better offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:53.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許他接了個更好的單
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria had Davis write
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞讓戴維斯為你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,a letter of recommendation in your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,寫了封推薦信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:59.54,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That must be where he realized that, if the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:59.54,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他一定是在那時意識到，一旦你倆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,were ever reunited, you would tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,重新聯手，你一定會告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,about his involvement with the missing generators.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,發電機丟失與他有關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.65,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Your asylum request has been denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.65,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你的庇護請求被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:10.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Your ride home</i> <i>departs in an hour.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:10.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一小時後送你回國
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:11.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,No, this is a mistake. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:11.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不，這樣不行，求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They'll kill me if I go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,回去他們會殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:22.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:22.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:23.43,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>I just sent you information</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:23.43,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>我剛發給你</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:25.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,on a new lead, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:25.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一條新線索的信息，偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It appears that Maria's boss redirected
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,看來瑪麗亞的老闆改變路線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,the missing generators in Iraq to an unknown destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,把伊拉克丟失的發電機轉運到未知的目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:31.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,How'd he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:31.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他怎麼做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.51,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but Omar knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.51,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不確定，但奧馬爾知情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:35.44,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Ken Davis arranged for him to be deported
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:35.44,chs_2,,0,0,0,,肯·戴維斯安排他遣送回伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:37.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>back to Iraq</i> <i>where he'll be killed.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:37.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>他會被殺的</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:38.78,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Davis doesn't have that kind of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:38.78,chs_2,,0,0,0,,戴維斯沒那種權力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:40.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>But he certainly has the resources</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:40.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>但他肯定有資源</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>to convince</i> <i>a corrupt UN diplomat</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>說服一個腐敗的聯合國外交官</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.35,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>to do his dirty work.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.35,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>幫他搞定</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:45.28,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I think I'm gonna have to pay Davis a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:45.28,chs_2,,0,0,0,,對，我覺得我得去拜訪一下戴維斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:46.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Please hurry, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:46.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,麻煩快點，偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>We haven't much time.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>我們沒多少時間了</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why would Davis steal the generators?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,戴維斯為什麼要偷發電機？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:52.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We're looking into that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:52.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們正在調查
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I have to get to Omar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我得去找奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:54.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:54.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你哪也不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,with the legionnaires still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,外籍士兵還在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:58.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Guy engineered this place with an armored door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:58.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這地方有裝甲門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:59.10,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and electromagnetic locks. You're safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:59.10,chs_2,,0,0,0,,和電磁鎖，你在這才安全
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.80,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.80,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:06.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They will kill Omar if he returns to Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:06.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,要是奧馬爾回到伊拉克，他們會殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:10.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:10.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:13.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:13.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你是要哭了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:15.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- What? - Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:15.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 什麼？\N- 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:17.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You and Omar were more than just business associates,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:17.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你跟奧馬爾不止是商業夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:21.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:21.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:28.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Every time I ran into a problem--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:28.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,每次我遇到麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:32.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,this sheikh, that tribe, this corrupt official--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:32.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,酋長，部落，貪官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:35.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,it was always Omar who solved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:35.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,都是奧馬爾解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:37.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,By bringing people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:37.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他把人聚到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:41.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's why I fell in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:41.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,所以我愛上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:45.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He would take me to the desert at night to drink cinnamon tea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:45.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他會在晚上帶我去沙漠喝肉桂茶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:49.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and count the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:49.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,數星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:52.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been to the desert at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:52.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你晚上去過沙漠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:54.28,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The only thing I remember about the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:54.28,chs_2,,0,0,0,,關於沙漠我只記得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:55.85,eng_1,,0,0,0,,is wiping the film
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:55.85,chs_2,,0,0,0,,要抹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,off the top of a warm glass of camel's milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,溫駱駝奶上面那層薄膜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:02.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's where the bacteria breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:02.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那是細菌繁殖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:05.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:05.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這建議不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:07.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:07.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我跟奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:10.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,we hoped to get married when he got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:10.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,希望在他來美國後結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:12.47,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He deserves asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:12.47,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他應該得到庇護
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:14.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I have to stop his deportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:14.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我得阻止他被驅逐出境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:15.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I need to get to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:15.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我得找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:17.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria, you have to trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:17.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞，你要相信我們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:20.67,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:20.67,chs_2,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:25.28,eng_1,,0,0,0,,My mother was an academic back in Iran.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:25.28,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我媽曾經是伊朗大學教師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.28,0:24:27.65,eng_1,,0,0,0,,When the Ayatollah and his fanatics
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.28,0:24:27.65,chs_2,,0,0,0,,1979年阿亞圖拉和他的狂熱分子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:30.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,took over in '79,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:30.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,武裝佔領伊朗時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.45,0:24:34.19,eng_1,,0,0,0,,someone risked his life smuggling my mom out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.45,0:24:34.19,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有人冒生命危險帶我媽偷渡出國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.19,0:24:37.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- If it weren't for him-- - You'd have never been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.19,0:24:37.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 要不是他…\N- 你就不會出生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.03,0:24:38.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Those fanatics
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.03,0:24:38.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那些
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.46,0:24:39.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,that could've killed my mom in Iran
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.46,0:24:39.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,在伊朗差點殺了我媽的狂熱分子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:42.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,are the same fanatics...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:42.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,跟伊拉克那些要殺奧馬爾的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:44.90,eng_1,,0,0,0,,that will kill Omar if he returns to Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:44.90,chs_2,,0,0,0,,狂熱分子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:46.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Just different stripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:46.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,只是兵種不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.54,0:24:48.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But we're not gonna let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.54,0:24:48.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但我們不會讓這事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.17,0:24:50.87,eng_1,,0,0,0,,How are you gonna stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.17,0:24:50.87,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你們要怎麼阻止？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.87,0:24:52.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Davis has a UN diplomat in his pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.87,0:24:52.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,戴維斯手上有個聯合國外交官
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:55.58,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and false accusations from the Iraqi government.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:55.58,chs_2,,0,0,0,,還有伊拉克政府的誣告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.58,0:24:57.58,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Did you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.58,0:24:57.58,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這個你讀了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.58,0:25:01.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,"According to a trusted source beyond reproach,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.58,0:25:01.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,「根據十分可靠的消息」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:04.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar Risha has ties to--"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:04.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,「奧馬爾·瑞捨勾結…」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.55,0:25:09.16,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.55,0:25:09.16,chs_2,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:10.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Davis's recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:10.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,戴維斯的推薦信？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:14.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,"Because of his impeccable integrity and trustworthiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:14.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,「鑒於其誠實守信的品質」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.83,0:25:17.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Omar is a man beyond reproach."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.83,0:25:17.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,「奧馬爾是十分可靠的人選」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:19.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Davis wrote both letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:19.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,兩封信都是戴維斯寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:21.87,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Iraqi government letterhead,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:21.87,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抬頭是伊拉克政府
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:23.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but the font and the...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:23.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但字體和…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.50,0:25:25.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,the format are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.50,0:25:25.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,版式是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.24,0:25:26.77,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He forged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.24,0:25:26.77,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這是他偽造的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.77,0:25:28.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And the original is in Lapointe's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.77,0:25:28.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,原件在拉普安特辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.18,0:25:29.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I have to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.18,0:25:29.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我得拿到它
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.84,0:25:31.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Oh, you can't get in there. - No, no, I know someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.84,0:25:31.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 你進不去的\N- 不，那裏有我認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:32.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- I know a way. - Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:32.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 我有辦法\N- 瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:36.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:36.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你哪也不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.18,0:25:40.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You have to trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.18,0:25:40.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你得相信我們
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.46,0:25:45.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yes, Maria Martinez is an employee of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.46,0:25:45.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,對，瑪麗亞·馬丁內斯是我的員工
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.06,0:25:47.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Something happen to her, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.06,0:25:47.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她出事了嗎，偵探？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.06,0:25:48.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You're a big energy guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.06,0:25:48.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你搞能源很有能耐，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.56,0:25:51.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,International businessman?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.56,0:25:51.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,國際商人？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.47,0:25:53.43,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Friends in high places?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.47,0:25:53.43,chs_2,,0,0,0,,在高層有朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.43,0:25:55.10,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Even the UN?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.43,0:25:55.10,chs_2,,0,0,0,,聯合國也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:57.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, I have a schedule to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:57.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不好意思，我有行程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:25:59.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:25:59.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.07,0:26:00.47,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You have another meeting scheduled
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.07,0:26:00.47,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你跟你聯合國的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.47,0:26:03.44,eng_1,,0,0,0,,with your friend inside the UN?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.47,0:26:03.44,chs_2,,0,0,0,,還要碰個面？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:07.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The one you've been calling every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:07.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,每天跟你打電話那人？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.11,0:26:08.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.11,0:26:08.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:11.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Metadata?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:11.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,元數據？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.75,0:26:13.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,This is a massive violation of my civil liberties.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.75,0:26:13.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這嚴重侵犯了我的公民自由
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.82,0:26:15.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Oh, we've already issued a warrant
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.82,0:26:15.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們已經申請了逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.25,0:26:16.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,for your corrupt French pal Lapointe
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.25,0:26:16.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,以企圖謀殺瑪麗亞·馬丁內斯的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.79,0:26:18.16,eng_1,,0,0,0,,for the attempted murder of Maria Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.79,0:26:18.16,chs_2,,0,0,0,,逮捕你那腐敗的法國朋友拉普安特
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:20.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,As soon as he flips,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:20.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一旦他落網
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.29,0:26:22.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,we'll have the forged document you sent to the UN
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.29,0:26:22.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們就會拿到那份你發到聯合國
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:24.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,naming Omar Risha a terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.83,0:26:24.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,指控奧馬爾·瑞捨為恐怖分子的偽造文件
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.46,0:26:26.73,eng_1,,0,0,0,,This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.46,0:26:26.73,chs_2,,0,0,0,,真荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.73,0:26:28.26,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Where's my attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.73,0:26:28.26,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我的律師在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.27,0:26:29.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,See, Omar found out about the generators.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.27,0:26:29.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾發現了發電機的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.84,0:26:32.34,eng_1,,0,0,0,,So you had him shipped back, knowing he'd be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.84,0:26:32.34,chs_2,,0,0,0,,所以你送他回去，讓他被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.34,0:26:34.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Then you tried to kill Maria too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.34,0:26:34.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,然後你想把瑪麗亞也殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.14,0:26:35.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Last I checked,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.14,0:26:35.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.24,0:26:37.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,your little NYPD fiefdom
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.24,0:26:37.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,區區紐約警局
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.58,0:26:38.81,eng_1,,0,0,0,,doesn't extend into the United Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.58,0:26:38.81,chs_2,,0,0,0,,還管不到聯合國
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.01,0:26:43.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Good luck using your tin badge to get in there, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.01,0:26:43.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,祝你順利用警徽進去，警探
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.18,0:26:45.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You really think you're a big shot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.18,0:26:45.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你真以為自己是大人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.25,0:26:47.92,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Get a couple bureaucrats in your pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.25,0:26:47.92,chs_2,,0,0,0,,手上有幾個官僚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.92,0:26:49.35,eng_1,,0,0,0,,grease the contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.92,0:26:49.35,chs_2,,0,0,0,,買兇殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.35,0:26:52.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You don't care who dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.35,0:26:52.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你不在乎別人的生死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.29,0:26:55.46,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Including your own employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.29,0:26:55.46,chs_2,,0,0,0,,包括你自己的員工
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.46,0:26:59.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Unless the DA's ready to charge my client, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.46,0:26:59.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,地方檢察官沒準備好起訴我的客戶的話，我們就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.70,0:27:02.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,If you're going to wade into international waters,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.70,0:27:02.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,如果你要涉水國際水域
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.60,0:27:06.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Detective, I suggest you get a bigger boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.60,0:27:06.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,警探，我建議你找艘更大的船
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.78,0:27:18.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Any word on Omar?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.78,0:27:18.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有奧馬爾的消息嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.32,0:27:27.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I could use a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.32,0:27:27.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我想喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.99,0:27:31.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,So could I.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.99,0:27:31.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.40,0:27:34.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,My boys keep a single malt in here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.40,0:27:34.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我哥們在這裏藏了瓶純麥酒
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.17,0:27:45.54,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thank God Finch buys top shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.17,0:27:45.54,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝天謝地，芬奇買了瓶高檔的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.15,0:28:00.42,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Finch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.15,0:28:00.42,chs_2,,0,0,0,,芬奇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.42,0:28:03.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Damn engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.42,0:28:03.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,該死的工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.33,0:28:15.90,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reese, they're loading Omar for deportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.33,0:28:15.90,chs_2,,0,0,0,,裏斯先生，他們要把奧馬爾驅逐出境了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.90,0:28:19.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.90,0:28:19.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們得有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.57,0:28:21.37,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.57,0:28:21.37,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我來跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.38,0:28:25.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>No need, Finch. I'm on it.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.38,0:28:25.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>不用，芬奇，我來處理</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.91,0:28:27.21,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.91,0:28:27.21,chs_2,,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.22,0:28:29.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.22,0:28:29.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.86,0:28:40.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Ms. Shaw, good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.86,0:28:40.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,肖女士，好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.09,0:28:41.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reese has rescued Omar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.09,0:28:41.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,裏斯先生已經救出奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.96,0:28:43.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.96,0:28:43.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.70,0:28:45.13,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Except we just lost Maria,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.70,0:28:45.13,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不過剛剛瑪麗亞跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.13,0:28:47.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and the legionnaires are still out there looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.13,0:28:47.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,外籍兵團還在外面找她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.20,0:28:49.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And what's worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.20,0:28:49.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,更糟糕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.27,0:28:50.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I think she's headed to Lapointe's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.27,0:28:50.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我覺得她去拉普安特辦公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.64,0:28:53.77,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Straight into the lion's den.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.64,0:28:53.77,chs_2,,0,0,0,,直入虎穴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.92,0:29:10.26,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Please, I have an appointment with Mr. Sevon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.92,0:29:10.26,chs_2,,0,0,0,,拜託，我跟斯萬先生有約
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.26,0:29:12.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He's a Greek diplomat. I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.26,0:29:12.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他是希臘外交官，我沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.06,0:29:13.26,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.06,0:29:13.26,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉，小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.26,0:29:14.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,No badge, no entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.26,0:29:14.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,沒有徽章不得入內
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:15.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What's the problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:15.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.86,0:29:17.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.86,0:29:17.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她是我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.57,0:29:20.97,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.57,0:29:20.97,chs_2,,0,0,0,,是，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.97,0:29:22.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.97,0:29:22.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們得快點
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.74,0:29:24.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria, when I said I'd help, I meant making a few calls--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.74,0:29:24.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞，我說能幫忙的意思是打電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.71,0:29:27.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Lapointe denied Omar's asylum based on a forged letter
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.71,0:29:27.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,拉普安特因為一封偽造的伊拉克政府的信
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.28,0:29:29.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,from the Iraqi government.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.28,0:29:29.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,拒絕庇護奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.14,0:29:31.54,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That letter is in Lapointe's office, and I need to get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.14,0:29:31.54,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那封信在拉普安特辦公室，我得拿到它
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.55,0:29:33.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.55,0:29:33.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.32,0:29:34.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We can't just break into the High Commissioner's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.32,0:29:34.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們不能闖進高級專員的辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.88,0:29:36.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,There are proper channels we can follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.88,0:29:36.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們可以通過適當的渠道解決
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.48,0:29:39.98,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Davis conspired with Lapointe to have Omar killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.48,0:29:39.98,chs_2,,0,0,0,,戴維斯和拉普安特要殺奧馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.99,0:29:41.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And now they want me dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.99,0:29:41.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,現在他們還想殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.46,0:29:43.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What? Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.46,0:29:43.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,什麼？他們為什麼這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.96,0:29:46.49,eng_1,,0,0,0,,To cover up the theft of six generators in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.96,0:29:46.49,chs_2,,0,0,0,,掩蓋在伊拉克偷了六台發電機的行徑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.49,0:29:48.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Look, I will explain the rest later,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.49,0:29:48.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,剩下的我一會再跟你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.09,0:29:51.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but right now I need to get that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.09,0:29:51.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,現在我得拿到那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.97,0:29:53.67,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'll take you as far as Lapointe's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.97,0:29:53.67,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我只能把你帶到拉普安特辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.67,0:29:56.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But then the rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.67,0:29:56.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,剩下的靠你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.24,0:29:58.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.24,0:29:58.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.81,0:30:05.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You're not a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.81,0:30:05.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你不是守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.11,0:30:06.68,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And you're not a terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.11,0:30:06.68,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你也不是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:08.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We know you saved Maria's life in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:08.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們知道你在伊拉克救了瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.75,0:30:10.61,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We're here to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.75,0:30:10.61,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們來這投桃報李
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.62,0:30:12.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's why you're helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.62,0:30:12.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你們就為此幫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.19,0:30:17.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Let's just say we all know what it's like to leave someone behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.19,0:30:17.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這麼說吧，我們都知道丟下某人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.96,0:30:19.09,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I love Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.96,0:30:19.09,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我愛瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.09,0:30:20.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,From the first time I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.09,0:30:20.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.99,0:30:22.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.99,0:30:22.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她現在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.86,0:30:24.13,eng_1,,0,0,0,,She's headed to the UN to get evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.86,0:30:24.13,chs_2,,0,0,0,,她去聯合國拿證據
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.13,0:30:26.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,to bring down Lapointe and Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.13,0:30:26.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,扳倒拉普安特和戴維斯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.03,0:30:28.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But not if they get to her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.03,0:30:28.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就怕他們先找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.20,0:30:30.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We'll we've got to get her out of there before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.20,0:30:30.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,趁還來得及，我們得帶她離開
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.00,0:30:32.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Are you really suggesting we break into the United Nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.00,0:30:32.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你真想讓我們闖進聯合國？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.14,0:30:34.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They have triple-layered security.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.14,0:30:34.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們有三重安保
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.01,0:30:36.21,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Infrared cameras</i> <i>with motion detection.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.01,0:30:36.21,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>帶運動檢測功能的紅外線攝像機</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.21,0:30:37.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.21,0:30:37.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我有個主意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.84,0:30:39.54,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But it's going to require a smoke screen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.84,0:30:39.54,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但需要煙幕
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.54,0:30:43.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and a big-ass truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.54,0:30:43.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,和一輛大卡車
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.72,0:30:52.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm in position outside the UN compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.72,0:30:52.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我已經在聯合國大樓外就位
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.73,0:31:04.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Gonna need to step on it, Reese.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.73,0:31:04.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,該行動了，裏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.50,0:31:08.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Ready on this end.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.50,0:31:08.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>這邊已就緒</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:12.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Open wide, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:12.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,散開點，小姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.65,0:31:20.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,There's a report of smoke on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.65,0:31:20.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,四樓報告有煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.48,0:31:21.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Call 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.48,0:31:21.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,打911
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.82,0:31:23.32,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Fire Department's already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.82,0:31:23.32,chs_2,,0,0,0,,消防隊已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.32,0:31:24.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We need to evacuate the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.32,0:31:24.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,大樓人員得撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:32.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Stop playing with the horn, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:32.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,別玩喇叭了，萊諾
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.83,0:31:34.36,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.83,0:31:34.36,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我從小
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.36,0:31:36.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to drive one of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.36,0:31:36.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就想開這種車
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:38.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Here, you're gonna need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:38.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,拿著，你會需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.18,0:31:47.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Have you told anyone about Lapointe?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.18,0:31:47.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你向別人提過拉普安特嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.84,0:31:51.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The original of the letter has to be here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.84,0:31:51.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,信的原件一定在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.42,0:31:54.58,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We should stop while we're ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.42,0:31:54.58,chs_2,,0,0,0,,現在收手還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:58.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I am not leaving until I clear Omar's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:58.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,奧馬爾罪名未洗，我是不會走的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.79,0:32:00.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Find anything on Davis, Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.79,0:32:00.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有戴維斯的信息嗎，芬奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.62,0:32:04.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Seems he's deleted all his email correspondence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.62,0:32:04.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,好像他刪除了所有的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.63,0:32:07.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Ms. Groves, I'm a bit occupied at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.63,0:32:07.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,葛洛弗女士，我現在有點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.53,0:32:09.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Try "Habur Gate," Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.53,0:32:09.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,試試「哈布爾河閘」，哈羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.57,0:32:10.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,"Habur Gate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.57,0:32:10.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,「哈布爾河閘」？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.63,0:32:12.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.63,0:32:12.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.27,0:32:13.80,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.27,0:32:13.80,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.80,0:32:16.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.80,0:32:16.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不過不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.24,0:32:18.07,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Oh, and, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.24,0:32:18.07,chs_2,,0,0,0,,噢，還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.14,0:32:22.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.14,0:32:22.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,借你的狗用用
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.38,0:32:31.99,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Customs clearance.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.38,0:32:31.99,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>報關單</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.99,0:32:33.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Six generators.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.99,0:32:33.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>6台發電機</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.72,0:32:35.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Requested by...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.72,0:32:35.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,訂貨人…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.32,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.32,chs_2,,0,0,0,,噢，不
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.07,0:32:46.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Where's the fire, <i>mes amis?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.07,0:32:46.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,火在哪，<i>朋友？</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.51,0:32:54.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.51,0:32:54.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.18,0:32:55.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- I found it. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.18,0:32:55.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 我找到了\N- 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.84,0:32:57.34,eng_1,,0,0,0,,We should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.84,0:32:57.34,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.35,0:33:00.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- He could be here any minute. - What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.35,0:33:00.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 他隨時會回來\N- 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.31,0:33:03.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I should have known it was you when I received a call from the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.31,0:33:03.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,警衛打來電話，我就知道是你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.45,0:33:05.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.45,0:33:05.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你在這裏幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:06.92,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Excusez-moi, Monsieur Lapointe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:06.92,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很抱歉，拉普安特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.32,0:33:11.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you spoke French.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.32,0:33:11.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你會說法語？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.86,0:33:14.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's the first thing they teach you in the Foreign Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.86,0:33:14.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,外籍兵團教的第一門課
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.66,0:33:36.50,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Consider this payback for what you did to my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.66,0:33:36.50,chs_2,,0,0,0,,就當這個是報復你害我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.50,0:33:39.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.50,0:33:39.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很好笑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.00,0:33:42.00,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Second round is always more accurate than the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.00,0:33:42.00,chs_2,,0,0,0,,第二發應該比第一發准
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.00,0:33:43.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What second round?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.00,0:33:43.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,什麼第二發？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.24,0:33:45.10,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You're not even holding a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.24,0:33:45.10,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你又沒有槍
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.11,0:33:47.17,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.11,0:33:47.17,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我說的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.86,0:34:05.43,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Excusez-moi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.86,0:34:05.43,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:16.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,So much for payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:16.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,報復到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.20,0:34:17.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.20,0:34:17.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.77,0:34:20.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.77,0:34:20.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,真可惜，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.27,0:34:21.77,eng_1,,0,0,0,,After all I did to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.27,0:34:21.77,chs_2,,0,0,0,,畢竟我幫過你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.78,0:34:24.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You're working with Davis? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.78,0:34:24.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你和戴維斯一夥的，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.31,0:34:26.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You don't understand how the real world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.31,0:34:26.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你不明白這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.05,0:34:30.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I learned a long time ago, as a legionnaire based in Rwanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.05,0:34:30.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,很久以前在盧旺達的兵團時，我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.05,0:34:33.08,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They used us to protect those who committed genocide.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.05,0:34:33.08,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們利用我們保護搞種族屠殺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.09,0:34:34.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Realpolitiks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.09,0:34:34.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,政治現實
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.55,0:34:36.79,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>This is about greed,</i> <i>not politics.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.55,0:34:36.79,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>這是貪婪，無關政治</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.79,0:34:38.16,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You have no loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.79,0:34:38.16,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你是牆頭草
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.16,0:34:41.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Look at where your loyalty has landed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.16,0:34:41.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你不是，卻走到了這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.83,0:34:44.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You know the worst thing about dying on a UN property?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.83,0:34:44.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你知道死在聯合國最糟糕的是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.23,0:34:46.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Extraterritorial privileges.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.23,0:34:46.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,治外法權
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.67,0:34:50.43,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Makes it very difficult for the NYPD to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.67,0:34:50.43,chs_2,,0,0,0,,紐約警察很難調查
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.50,0:34:54.14,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Somebody call 911?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.50,0:34:54.14,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有人打911？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.14,0:34:55.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Drop the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.14,0:34:55.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,放下槍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:57.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Or what, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:57.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不然怎樣，警官？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.01,0:35:00.28,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Or I'm gonna get <i>Realpolitik-y</i> <i>on your ass.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.01,0:35:00.28,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不然我就<i>現實地踢你屁股</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.35,0:35:04.01,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You and Davis stole the generators from Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.35,0:35:04.01,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你和戴維斯從伊拉克偷了發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.02,0:35:06.12,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You have no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.02,0:35:06.12,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你沒有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.12,0:35:08.68,eng_1,,0,0,0,,"Habur Gate" ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.12,0:35:08.68,chs_2,,0,0,0,,「哈布爾河閘」，聽說過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.69,0:35:13.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Habur Gate. That's</i> <i>the border crossing</i> between Iraq and Turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.69,0:35:13.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>哈布爾河閘，在伊拉克和土耳其邊界</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.69,0:35:18.36,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Next time have someone else sign the customs form.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.69,0:35:18.36,chs_2,,0,0,0,,下次找別人簽報關單
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.10,0:35:23.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Go figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.10,0:35:23.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,原來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.60,0:35:26.77,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Turns out immunity doesn't stop you from bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.60,0:35:26.77,chs_2,,0,0,0,,豁免權也止不住你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.34,0:35:31.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's what I call diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.34,0:35:31.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這就是外交
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.94,0:35:33.84,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.94,0:35:33.84,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.85,0:35:36.45,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, I can't believe you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.85,0:35:36.45,chs_2,,0,0,0,,上帝啊，不敢相信你來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.45,0:35:38.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Gonna need to step it up, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.45,0:35:38.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,快點吧，夥計們
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.48,0:35:41.72,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sounds like the cavalry's on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.48,0:35:41.72,chs_2,,0,0,0,,好像援兵到了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.72,0:35:43.49,eng_1,,0,0,0,,- Come on. Let's go. - We gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.72,0:35:43.49,chs_2,,0,0,0,,- 來吧，快走\N- 得走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.03,0:36:00.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,How'd you find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.03,0:36:00.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼找到這裏的？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.24,0:36:03.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Someone recommended the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.24,0:36:03.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有人說景色好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.15,0:36:09.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,The office of the High Commissioner
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.15,0:36:09.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,高級專員辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.48,0:36:12.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,just sent this over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.48,0:36:12.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,剛送來這個
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.32,0:36:14.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.32,0:36:14.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.05,0:36:15.52,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Your asylum's officially been approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.05,0:36:15.52,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你的避難申請批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.32,0:36:20.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And Sevon?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.32,0:36:20.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,斯萬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.56,0:36:22.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Greece revoked his diplomatic immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.56,0:36:22.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,希臘取消了他的外交豁免權
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.76,0:36:26.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,NYPD arrested him for the murder of Lapointe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.76,0:36:26.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,紐約警察以謀殺拉普安特的罪名逮捕了他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.53,0:36:29.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Detective, and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.53,0:36:29.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝你，警官，還有你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.70,0:36:31.23,eng_1,,0,0,0,,For everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.70,0:36:31.23,chs_2,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.23,0:36:34.43,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Welcome to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.23,0:36:34.43,chs_2,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到紐約！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.61,0:36:46.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.61,0:36:46.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,嘿，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.42,0:36:47.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Thought the case was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.42,0:36:47.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我以為結案了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.95,0:36:51.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You did good tonight, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.95,0:36:51.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你今晚不錯啊，萊諾
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.62,0:36:53.42,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Glass of champagne, best you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.62,0:36:53.42,chs_2,,0,0,0,,來杯最好的香檳
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.42,0:36:55.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.42,0:36:55.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我以為你不喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.26,0:36:59.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,March 20th.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.26,0:36:59.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,3月20號
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.56,0:37:02.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Persian New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.56,0:37:02.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,波斯新年
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:06.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't care about foreign cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:06.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我以為你不關心異國文化
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.03,0:37:08.53,eng_1,,0,0,0,,That's what's great about New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.03,0:37:08.53,chs_2,,0,0,0,,紐約的妙處就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.54,0:37:11.44,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You don't have to travel to learn about other cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.54,0:37:11.44,chs_2,,0,0,0,,瞭解文化不用出門
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.44,0:37:14.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They all come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.44,0:37:14.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,它們在這裏彙集
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.41,0:37:17.41,eng_1,,0,0,0,,My father brought my mother here on their first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.41,0:37:17.41,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我父親第一次約會我母親就是在這
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.41,0:37:20.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.41,0:37:20.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.05,0:37:21.55,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.05,0:37:21.55,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.55,0:37:24.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It's changed names a couple times,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.55,0:37:24.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,改了幾次名字
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.05,0:37:27.29,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but the view's still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.05,0:37:27.29,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但景色還是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.29,0:37:33.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Get outta here, Fusco.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.29,0:37:33.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你走吧，法斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.06,0:37:37.69,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Happy new year, Sameen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.06,0:37:37.69,chs_2,,0,0,0,,新年快樂，薩敏
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.33,0:37:42.80,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It may not be the desert stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.33,0:37:42.80,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許不是沙漠的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:45.30,eng_1,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing like the New York City skyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:45.30,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但紐約的夜色無與倫比
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.85,0:38:03.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>And Davis?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.85,0:38:03.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>戴維斯呢？</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.16,0:38:04.26,eng_1,,0,0,0,,According to Detective Fusco,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.16,0:38:04.26,chs_2,,0,0,0,,據法斯克警探說
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.26,0:38:05.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,he's flown the coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.26,0:38:05.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.83,0:38:09.16,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And with his international connections...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.83,0:38:09.16,chs_2,,0,0,0,,有這麼多海外關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.16,0:38:10.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,he could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.16,0:38:10.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他選擇很多
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.63,0:38:13.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Maybe one of our allies will scoop him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.63,0:38:13.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也許我們的盟友會挖出他來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.70,0:38:16.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Speaking of allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.70,0:38:16.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,說到盟友…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.03,0:38:20.20,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I do hope that Root isn't feeding Bear any chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.03,0:38:20.20,chs_2,,0,0,0,,但願根姐別喂大熊巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.34,0:38:27.94,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sit. Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.34,0:38:27.94,chs_2,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.68,0:38:33.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I've secured the generators you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.68,0:38:33.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我搞到了你要的發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.15,0:38:34.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,They shipped from Akcaabat Port last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.15,0:38:34.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,上周已經從阿克恰阿巴德港發貨了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.89,0:38:37.32,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to power? New York City?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.89,0:38:37.32,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你想為什麼供電？紐約？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.32,0:38:40.32,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear about your friend Sevon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.32,0:38:40.32,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你朋友斯萬的事，我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.33,0:38:43.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But just as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.33,0:38:43.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不過也好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.33,0:38:46.56,eng_1,,0,0,0,,He worked for an antiquated institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.33,0:38:46.56,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他效命的組織很古老
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.56,0:38:49.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hard to believe that Nation States still think
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.56,0:38:49.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,難以相信聯合國還認為
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.33,0:38:51.40,eng_1,,0,0,0,,they have any influence, even in cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.33,0:38:51.40,chs_2,,0,0,0,,他們還有影響力，還能合作
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.40,0:38:53.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sevon got sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.40,0:38:53.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,斯萬失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:56.74,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I can't afford such liabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:56.74,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我承受不了這種紕漏
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.74,0:38:58.64,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Then lucky for me I'm careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.74,0:38:58.64,chs_2,,0,0,0,,幸運的是我很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.64,0:39:02.24,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.64,0:39:02.24,chs_2,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.99,0:39:20.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.99,0:39:20.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.28,0:39:36.51,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Go blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.28,0:39:36.51,chs_2,,0,0,0,,關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.88,0:40:15.82,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Which way, Bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.88,0:40:15.82,chs_2,,0,0,0,,哪邊，大熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.59,0:40:20.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.59,0:40:20.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:45.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ms. Groves.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:45.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你好，葛洛弗女士
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.58,0:40:46.91,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sit, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.58,0:40:46.91,chs_2,,0,0,0,,坐下，小子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.91,0:40:50.52,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I commend your tracking abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.91,0:40:50.52,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我讚賞你的跟蹤技能
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.85,0:40:54.49,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Sense of smell is often the most neglected of the five senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.85,0:40:54.49,chs_2,,0,0,0,,五感中，嗅覺最容易被忽視
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.49,0:40:57.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And one which machines can't replicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.49,0:40:57.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這一點機器也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.62,0:41:02.26,eng_1,,0,0,0,,At least... not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.62,0:41:02.26,chs_2,,0,0,0,,起碼…目前沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.26,0:41:05.96,eng_1,,0,0,0,,When I was a boy, we had a foxhound called--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.26,0:41:05.96,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我小時候，有只獵狐犬名叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.97,0:41:08.60,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Churchill.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.97,0:41:08.60,chs_2,,0,0,0,,丘吉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:13.73,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Shall we cut to the chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:13.73,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們開門見山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.34,0:41:17.48,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You have some things that don't belong to you--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.34,0:41:17.48,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你偷了點東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.48,0:41:21.65,eng_1,,0,0,0,,two hard drives, a superconducting chip,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.48,0:41:21.65,chs_2,,0,0,0,,兩塊硬盤，一個超級芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.65,0:41:23.11,eng_1,,0,0,0,,and six generators.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.65,0:41:23.11,chs_2,,0,0,0,,6台發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.12,0:41:25.62,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Which means,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.12,0:41:25.62,chs_2,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.62,0:41:29.15,eng_1,,0,0,0,,either your planning to bring Samaritan online...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.62,0:41:29.15,chs_2,,0,0,0,,要不你在計劃使撒瑪利亞上線
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.15,0:41:31.89,eng_1,,0,0,0,,or you're the world's most ambitious gamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.15,0:41:31.89,chs_2,,0,0,0,,要不你就是世界最大的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.89,0:41:35.03,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Why waste time arguing about small battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.89,0:41:35.03,chs_2,,0,0,0,,何必為小衝突浪費口舌
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.03,0:41:38.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,when we could be discussing the larger war?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.03,0:41:38.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我們可以談談更大的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.06,0:41:42.57,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you and I have more in common than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.06,0:41:42.57,chs_2,,0,0,0,,或許你我的共同點比你想像的要多
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.57,0:41:44.33,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.57,0:41:44.33,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.34,0:41:46.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I want the machine to be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.34,0:41:46.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我想要機器自由
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.71,0:41:48.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,You wanna control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.71,0:41:48.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你想控制它
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.31,0:41:51.88,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I won't bore you with academic theories
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.31,0:41:51.88,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不想用沉悶的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.88,0:41:54.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,about competing civilizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.88,0:41:54.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,解釋文明的競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.38,0:41:57.75,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It's human nature to want to control the means
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.38,0:41:57.75,chs_2,,0,0,0,,人類的本性就是控制渠道獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.75,0:41:59.38,eng_1,,0,0,0,,to wealth, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.75,0:41:59.38,chs_2,,0,0,0,,財富，嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.39,0:42:02.89,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Whether it be salt or gold or oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.39,0:42:02.89,chs_2,,0,0,0,,無論是鹽，金子或者石油
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.89,0:42:04.25,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Or information.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.89,0:42:04.25,chs_2,,0,0,0,,抑或是信息
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.26,0:42:06.02,eng_1,,0,0,0,,It is the new currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.26,0:42:06.02,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這是新通貨
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.02,0:42:08.39,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And if someone's gonna control it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.02,0:42:08.39,chs_2,,0,0,0,,如果有人要控制
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.39,0:42:10.66,eng_1,,0,0,0,,it might as well be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.39,0:42:10.66,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不如乾脆是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.66,0:42:12.76,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.66,0:42:12.76,chs_2,,0,0,0,,想像一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.76,0:42:16.83,eng_1,,0,0,0,,what it would be like to merge, permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.76,0:42:16.83,chs_2,,0,0,0,,聯手起來會如何，永久的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.84,0:42:19.54,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I could use someone with such capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.84,0:42:19.54,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我需要有能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.54,0:42:21.27,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.54,0:42:21.27,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我為什麼要合作？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.27,0:42:25.77,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Because I know what you know to be true, Ms. Groves, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.27,0:42:25.77,chs_2,,0,0,0,,因為我知道你所知不假，葛洛弗女士
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.78,0:42:27.58,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Everyone thinks you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.78,0:42:27.58,chs_2,,0,0,0,,大家都以為你瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.58,0:42:29.05,eng_1,,0,0,0,,But I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.58,0:42:29.05,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我不這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.05,0:42:32.85,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Because we understand what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.05,0:42:32.85,chs_2,,0,0,0,,因為我們知道未來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.85,0:42:35.18,eng_1,,0,0,0,,What's about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.85,0:42:35.18,chs_2,,0,0,0,,將會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.19,0:42:37.85,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.19,0:42:37.85,chs_2,,0,0,0,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.86,0:42:40.86,eng_1,,0,0,0,,And what makes you think you're in any position
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.86,0:42:40.86,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你憑什麼以為你有資格
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:42.89,eng_1,,0,0,0,,to negotiate?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:42.89,chs_2,,0,0,0,,討價還價？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.07,0:42:50.70,eng_1,,0,0,0,,<i>Touche.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.07,0:42:50.70,chs_2,,0,0,0,,<i>不錯啊</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.70,0:42:53.63,eng_1,,0,0,0,,I never feel civilized...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.70,0:42:53.63,chs_2,,0,0,0,,我一直覺得很不文明
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.64,0:42:57.04,eng_1,,0,0,0,,negotiating from the end of a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.64,0:42:57.04,chs_2,,0,0,0,,談判時被人用槍威脅…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.04,0:43:00.31,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Either end.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.04,0:43:00.31,chs_2,,0,0,0,,或用槍威脅別人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.31,0:43:03.06,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Shall we call this one a draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.31,0:43:03.06,chs_2,,0,0,0,,這次算平手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.98,0:43:05.81,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.98,0:43:05.81,chs_2,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.82,0:43:07.95,eng_1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps next time we meet
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.82,0:43:07.95,chs_2,,0,0,0,,或許下次我們再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.95,0:43:10.68,eng_1,,0,0,0,,you'll reconsider my offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.95,0:43:10.68,chs_2,,0,0,0,,你會重新考慮我的提議

